abstract: Mikheil Saakashvili resigns as governor of Ukraine's Odessa region, accusing Pres Petro O Poroshenko of supporting corruption.

headline.print_headline: Former Georgian Leader Quits His Reform Effort in Ukraine, Citing Corruption
headline.main: Mikheil Saakashvili Resigns Post in Ukraine, Citing Corruption

snippet: The former president of Georgia quit his post as governor of the Odessa region, accusing the Ukrainian president of blocking efforts to root out graft....
lead_paragraph: The former president of Georgia quit his post as governor of the Odessa region, accusing the Ukrainian president of blocking efforts to root out graft.
